# UI Update, Menu Reorganization, and Store Integration

This plan covers removing Winlator branding, cleaning up headers, reorganizing the main menu, implementing multi-store integration (Steam, Epic, GOG, Amazon), and designing a professional application icon.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name] Layouts and UI

#### [MODIFY] [main_activity.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/layout/main_activity.xml)
- Remove `app:headerLayout="@layout/main_menu_header"` from `NavigationView` to eliminate Winlator logo.
- Remove the `Toolbar` view for a cleaner header.

#### [MODIFY] [containers_fragment.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/layout/containers_fragment.xml)
- Remove the legacy `BTAddContainer` text button.
- Add a modern `FloatingActionButton` (FAB) for container creation.

#### [NEW] [stores_fragment.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/layout/stores_fragment.xml)
- UI for the "Stores" view, featuring cards for Steam, Epic, GOG, and Amazon with Sign In/Out buttons.

#### [NEW] [ic_win_launcher.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/drawable/ic_win_launcher.xml)
- Professional application icon design reflecting the "WinNative" identity.

### [Component Name] Navigation and Logic

#### [MODIFY] [main_menu.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/menu/main_menu.xml)
- Reorder and rename items:
    1. Stores (New)
    2. Presets (Renamed from Settings)
    3. Components (Renamed from Contents)
    4. Drivers (Renamed from Adrenotools GPU)
    5. Input Controls

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.java](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/MainActivity.java)
