#### [NEW] [StoresFragment.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/StoresFragment.kt)
- Logic for handling multi-store authentication and state management.

#### [NEW] [Service Porting]
- Port [EpicService.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/Reference/GameNative/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/service/epic/EpicService.kt), [GOGService.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/Reference/GameNative/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/service/gog/GOGService.kt), and [AmazonService.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/Reference/GameNative/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/service/amazon/AmazonService.kt) from `Reference/GameNative` to `WinNative`.

### [Component Name] Strings

#### [MODIFY] [strings.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/values/strings.xml)
